'''Domain Tivvik''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], Domain Tivvik's vessels were part of the flotilla sent to attack [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]]. [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commander]] [[Tivvik]] was a member, as was the [[Intendant caste|intendant]] [[Fal Tivvik]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

